<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Bot Name</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .headline, .features, .description, .about, .contact, .faqs {
            background: rgba(4, 0, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .headline:hover, .features:hover, .description:hover, .about:hover, .contact:hover, .faqs:hover {
            transform: scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #3c10ff;
        }
        p, li {
            color: #CCC;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            background-color: #111;
            color: #DDD;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="headline">
            <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: #ffffff;">NEXUS</span></h1>
            <p>The ultimate Discord bot for enhancing your server's experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <p>Discover what makes our bot unique:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Advanced Moderation</li>
                <li>Customizable Welcome Messages</li>
                <li>Music Streaming</li>
                <li>Fun and Games</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <h2>Description</h2>
            <p>Your Discord bot, <strong>Your Bot Name</strong>, is designed to enrich your Discord server's community by providing a variety of features...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>We are a team of passionate developers dedicated to creating engaging experiences on Discord. Learn more about our journey and what motivates us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact">
            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            <p>Have questions or need support? Get in touch with us:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email: contact@toowake.dev</li>
                <li>Discord: <a style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none;" href="https://discord.gg/toowake-dev-hosting-1121353922355929129">TOOWAKE.DEV</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="live-stats">
            <h2>Live Stats</h2>
            <% if (liveStats) { %>
                <div class="stat-item">Total Servers: <%= liveStats.totalServers %></div>
                <div class="stat-item">Active Users: <%= liveStats.activeUsers %></div>
                <div class="stat-item">Commands Processed: <%= liveStats.commandsProcessed %></div>
            <% } else { %>
                <p>Live stats are currently unavailable.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Bot Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
